{"id":7027,"content":"<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:chsdate Year=\"2010\" Month=\"2\" Day=\"26\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\" w:st=\"on\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2010</FONT><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;\" lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>年</SPAN></SPAN><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2</FONT><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;\" lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>月</SPAN></SPAN><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">26</FONT><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;\" lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>日</SPAN></SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;\" lang=EN-US>农历正月十三，炎黄春秋杂志社全体工作人员与本刊顾问、编委、作者和热心读者</SPAN><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">100</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">余人，在北京举办了一场气氛十分活跃的“炎黄春秋新春联谊会”。近</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">20</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">位德高望重的老前辈、老专家学者、卓有成就的中青年学者以及热心作者、读者在联谊会上作了热情洋溢的发言。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">新春联谊会由</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">由执行社长</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">、总编辑吴思主持。他首先代表杂志社向与会的老朋友们拜了个晚年，并简单扼要地介绍了《炎黄春秋》杂志</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>2009</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">年各项工作的完成情况。吴思同时向大家报告了一个好消息：由于与会朋友以及广大读者和作者的鼎力支持和热情关注，《炎黄春秋》杂志</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>2010</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">年度订阅量比</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>2009</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">年度再度大幅攀升，升幅突破</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US>10%</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">韩钢、王海光、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">李锐、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">丁东、何方、资中筠、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">江平、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">杜光、李昌平、章立凡、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">冯健、李维民、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">孙大午、张思之等</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">先后在<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">联谊会上</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">发言。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">社长杜导正最后也作了</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">精彩的讲话。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">出席新春联谊会的各界来宾为（以下名单顺序按姓氏笔画排列）：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">丁<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN>东、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">马立诚、马仲廉、马国川、王也扬、王</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">才、王克明、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">王宏志、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">王金凤、<BR>王俊义、王海光、王强华、冯 </SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">健、刘 </SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">玉、刘仰东、刘志琴、孙大午、朱</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">良、<BR>江</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">平、牟广平、纪希晨、何 </SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">方、余焕椿、吴</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">象、吴</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">薇、宋以敏、张天来、<BR>张秀平、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">张 </SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">鸣、张思之、张培森、张惠卿、李 </SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">乔、李 </SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">杨、李宝光、李昌平、<BR></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">李树桥、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">李耐因、李胜平、李维民、李 </SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">普、李 </SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">锐、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">杜<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN>光、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">杨天石、杨</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">杰、<BR>苏双碧、谷秀敏、辛子陵、邵燕祥、陈国华、陈震峰、周良宵、季</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5p